opinions.text:
ORDER
Since the order which petitioner asks us to review is interlocutory, the petition for writ of certiorari is denied.

attorneys: Goldberg, Goldberg & Goldberg, Robert D. Goldberg, Pawtucket, for petitioner.
Gunning, LaFazia & Gnys, Inc., Robert W. Smith, Providence, for respondent.
